      <title>拉皮丹称石油市场对伊朗制裁风险“掉以轻心”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/oil-market-is-complacent-to-iran-sanctions-risks-rapidan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rapidan Energy Group 总裁鲍勃麦克纳利表示，石油市场对于伊朗和俄罗斯制裁加剧前景带来的地缘政治风险“仍然感到自满”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/oil-market-is-complacent-to-iran-sanctions-risks-rapidan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 17:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贡渥鹿特丹炼油厂加入欧洲停产名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/gunvor-s-rotterdam-oil-refinery-joins-list-of-european-shutdowns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于盈利不足，贡渥集团 (Gunvor Group) 暂停了其位于鹿特丹的炼油厂运营，这是欧洲大陆的炼油厂难以与世界其他地区的新兴炼油厂竞争的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/gunvor-s-rotterdam-oil-refinery-joins-list-of-european-shutdowns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 17:33:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大丰业银行呼吁客户在税收损失销售季节到来前转换交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/scotiabank-urges-switch-trades-ahead-of-tax-loss-selling-season</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着税收损失销售季节的临近，加拿大丰业银行建议在一年中转换交易，因为广泛的收益需要采取更有针对性的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/scotiabank-urges-switch-trades-ahead-of-tax-loss-selling-season</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 17:31:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
