      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 14:34:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>避险需求推动黄金价格创 20 个月来最大周涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/gold-xauusd-holds-four-day-gain-on-haven-demand-and-dovish-fed-comments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于俄罗斯与乌克兰冲突升级增强了黄金的避险吸引力，且交易员也在评估美联储进一步放松政策的前景，黄金有望创下自去年 3 月以来的最大单周涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/gold-xauusd-holds-four-day-gain-on-haven-demand-and-dovish-fed-comments</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 00:22:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗、俄罗斯地缘政治紧张局势加剧，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于俄罗斯和伊朗等地缘政治紧张局势加剧，同时股市走强增加了风险资产的吸引力，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 23:34:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
